# Evidence

This folder contains screenshots and configuration exports captured during the assessment of default Azure and GCP IaaS environments.

## Contents

### Azure
- `az-nsg-flow-logs-disabled.png` — Default NSG configuration showing flow logs not enabled
- `az-storage-public-access.png` — Default storage account with public blob access enabled
- `az-vm-diagnostics-off.png` — Default VM diagnostic settings showing logs not configured
- `az-defender-default-score.png` — Defender for Cloud default security score on fresh subscription

### GCP
- `gcp-default-sa-editor-role.png` — Default Compute Engine SA with Editor role binding
- `gcp-vpc-flow-logs-off.png` — Default subnet configuration with flow logging disabled
- `gcp-firewall-rules-no-logging.png` — Default VPC firewall rules without logging enabled
- `gcp-scc-default-findings.png` — Security Command Center default findings on fresh project

---

*Screenshots captured from test environments provisioned with default settings. No post-provisioning changes were applied prior to capture.*
